---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="SEO & Performance | Engenharia e Code" description="Estratégias de SEO Técnico e Otimização de Web Performance (WPO).">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
		<header class="mb-12">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">SEO & Performance</h1>
			<p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">
				A visibilidade não é nada sem performance. Minha abordagem une SEO Técnico rigoroso com otimizações de Core Web Vitals para garantir que seu conteúdo seja encontrado e entregue instantaneamente.
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
			<!-- Performance Card -->
			<section class="bg-slate-800/20 border border-slate-700 p-8 rounded-2xl">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v4"/><path d="m16.2 7.8 2.9-2.9"/><path d="M18 12h4"/><path d="m16.2 16.2 2.9 2.9"/><path d="M12 18v4"/><path d="m4.9 19.1 2.9-2.9"/><path d="M2 12h4"/><path d="m4.9 4.9 2.9 2.9"/></svg>
					Web Performance
				</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-300">
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<span class="text-emerald-500 font-bold">100</span>
						<span><strong>Lighthouse Perfect Scores:</strong> Foco em atingir métricas verdes em Performance, Acessibilidade e Best Practices.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<span class="text-emerald-500 font-bold">0kb</span>
						<span><strong>Zero JS Baseline:</strong> Uso de Astro para enviar HTML estático puro, hidratando componentes apenas quando necessário (Islands).</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<span class="text-emerald-500 font-bold">WPO</span>
						<span><strong>Asset Optimization:</strong> Pipelines automáticos que convertem imagens para AVIF/WebP e minificam CSS/JS.</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<!-- SEO Card -->
			<section class="bg-slate-800/20 border border-slate-700 p-8 rounded-2xl">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg>
					SEO Técnico
				</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-300">
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<span class="text-blue-500">JSON-LD</span>
						<span><strong>Dados Estruturados:</strong> Implementação schemna.org para Rich Snippets (Breadcrumbs, Articles, FAQs).</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<span class="text-blue-500">Meta</span>
						<span><strong>Tags Semânticas:</strong> Arquitetura de cabeçalho correta (H1-H6), tags canônicas e Open Graph automático.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<span class="text-blue-500">Sitemap</span>
						<span><strong>Geração Automática:</strong> Sitemaps XML e robots.txt integrados ao pipeline de build.</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
		</div>

		<!-- Case Study Highlight -->
		<section class="border-t border-slate-800 pt-12">
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
				<div class="flex-1">
					<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Case Real: +300% Tráfego Orgânico</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">
						Descubra como apliquei essas técnicas em um e-commerce real para reverter uma queda de posicionamento e superar competidores.
					</p>
					<a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}projetos/seo-optimization`} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors">
						Ler Case Study
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
					</a>
				</div>
				<div class="flex-1 bg-slate-900 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 font-mono text-sm text-slate-400">
					<div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-800 pb-2 mb-4">
						<span>Audit Report</span>
						<span class="text-emerald-500">Passed</span>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-3">
						<div class="flex justify-between">
							<span>First Contentful Paint</span>
							<span class="text-emerald-400">0.8s</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex justify-between">
							<span>Speed Index</span>
							<span class="text-emerald-400">1.2s</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex justify-between">
							<span>Largest Contentful Paint</span>
							<span class="text-emerald-400">1.5s</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex justify-between">
							<span>Cumulative Layout Shift</span>
							<span class="text-emerald-400">0.002</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>
